title: Nissan car sales in Europe 2003 to 2018
summary: In general Number of units sold has rose over the Year.
Number of units sold is roughly constant from 2004 to 2005, slightly decreasing from 2005 to 2006, roughly constant from 2006 to 2007, and finally gradually increasing from 2007 to 2011.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
Maximum Number of units sold, about 470004.0 was reported at Year 2011
The lowest Number of units sold, of value 313437.0 was reported at Year 2007
